sequenceDiagram
    participant Consumer
    participant Broker as Pact Broker
    participant Provider

    Consumer->>Broker: 1. Publish contract<br/>(expected requests/responses)
    Provider->>Broker: 2. Fetch contract
    Provider->>Provider: 3. Verify contract<br/>against real implementation
    Provider->>Broker: 4. Report verification result
    Broker-->>Consumer: 5. Can I deploy? (check compatibility)
